node.title: Man missing for three weeks found dead
node.description: A 64-year-old man recently reported missing on the West Coast, has been found dead.
node.content:
["A 64-year-old man recently reported missing on the West Coast, has been found dead.", "", "
File pic Photo: 123rf
", "Hugh Cameron was last seen in Runanga more than three weeks ago, on 21 March.", "Police made an appeal for information about Cameron on 25 March, expressing concerns for his welfare.", "His death is not being considered suspicious and will be referred to the Coroner.", "Police would like to thank Kotuku Surf Club and the local rescue helicopter for their assistance."]
